  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "As part of the new component library effort we're introducing a new component `StatusIcon` that simply renders icons in desired colors and rotation orientation.\r\n\r\nIcons are used in many places throughout the app, mostly using `SVGImage`, which we probably get rid off in the mid-term. Once #2330 lands we should replace the usages of `SVGImage` for icons using `StatusIcon`.\r\n\r\nThis includes buttons like `StatusRoundButton`, `StatusIconButton`, `StatusButton` etc and possibly others.\r\n\r\nThe main reason the usage of `StatusIcon` hasn't been introduced as part of #2330 yet is that some components make custom use of `SVGImage` and need to be reviewed specifically.",
